%3B%20rate%20cuts%20of%20100-basis%20points%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CME%20FedWatch%20Tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20US%20economy%20sees%20a%20strong%20rebound%20from%20the%20weak%20July%20jobs%20report%2C%20it%20could%20drive%20a%20sentiment%20change%20in%20the%20market%20and%20prove%20that%20investors%20are%20overly%20confident%20in%20the%20Fed's%20rate%20cut%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20note%2C%20this%20would%20likely%20put%20downward%20pressure%20on%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20as%20Kwon%20recommended%20investors%20hedge%20the%20downside%20risk%20with%20October%20put%20spreads%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20signs%20of%20a%20resilient%20economy%20include%20second-quarter%20GDP%20growth%20being%20revised%20higher%20to%203.0%25%20from%202.8%25%2C%20as%20well%20as%20solid%20personal%20spending%20data%2C%20which%20jumped%200.5%25%20month-over-month%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20continues%20to%20disprove%20skeptics.%20Growth%20has%20certainly%20cooled%20relative%20to%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it%20has%20done%20so%20at%20a%20gradual%20pace%2C%26quot%3B%20Kwon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Wall%20Street%20strategist%20who%20expects%20a%20hot%20jobs%20report%20on%20Friday%20is%20Ed%20Yardeni%20of%20Yardeni%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20on%20Monday%2C%20Yardeni%20said%20he%20expects%20200%2C000%20to%20225%2C000%20jobs%20were%20added%20to%20the%20economy%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20accurate%2C%20this%20would%20blow%20away%20economist%20estimates%20and%20align%20with%20the%20strong%20jobs%20reports%20seen%20in%20May%20and%20June%2C%20playing%20into%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20Fed%20doesn't%20need%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20all%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unlikely%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20have%20to%20lower%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%20as%20rapidly%20and%20by%20as%20much%20as%20was%20necessary%20during%20previous%20monetary%20easing%20cycles%20when%20financial%20crises%20triggered%20credit%20crunches%20and%20recessions%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Yardeni's%20optimistic%20outlook%20would%20be%20great%20news%20for%20the%20economy%2C%20it%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20headwind%20for%20stock%20prices%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-biggest-risk-this-week-hot-august-jobs-report-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725392065000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d74bc414a5cd1fcc8cc29a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-biggest-risk-this-week-hot-august-jobs-report-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEquities%20seem%20more%20excited%20about%20the%20cuts%20than%20concerned%20about%20a%20potential%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20strategists%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-biggest-risk-this-week-hot-august-jobs-report-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22C%20Sankaran%20Nair%20biopic%20eyeing%20early%202025%20release%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725391992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113040553%2Cimgsize-48650.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-and-karan-johars-biopic-on-c-sankaran-nair-eyeing-early-2025-release%2Farticleshow%2F113040553.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5