A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Felton-john-severe-eye-infection-recovering-vision-1236128909%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20and%20worker%20well-being%20are%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20business%20leaders%2C%20according%20to%20execs%20from%20Accenture%2C%20Mastercard%2C%20Ancestry%2C%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workforce%20Innovation%20Series%20template%20with%20vertical%2C%20colorful%20stripes%20on%20the%20left%20and%20bottom%20sides.%20A%20blue-tinted%20photo%20of%20a%20group%20of%20people%20sitting%20around%20a%20table%20in%20a%20professional%20meeting%20is%20featured%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d1e1941d8d2deb96b7b660%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Andrius%20Banelis%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20from%2010%20companies%20who%20are%20participants%20in%20our%20first-ever%20Workforce%20Innovation%20Board%20convened%20for%20a%20virtual%20roundtable%20on%20August%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20asked%20to%20share%20which%20topics%20they're%20most%20focused%20on%20between%20AI%2C%20worker%20well-being%2C%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20and%20C-suite%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20worker%20well-being%20and%20AI%20were%20the%20most%20commonly%20cited%20trends%2C%20there's%20clear%20overlap%20and%20intersectionality%20across%20all%20four%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuccessful%20employees%20need%20training%20and%20support%2C%20equitable%20and%20fair%20access%20to%20opportunities%2C%20and%20reassurances%20about%20the%20integration%20of%20AI.%20C-suite%20leaders%2C%20facing%20internal%20and%20external%20scrutiny%20and%20pressures%2C%20need%20a%20productive%20and%20motivated%20workforce%2C%20and%20to%20organize%20in%20new%20ways%20to%20enable%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20inflection%20point%20is%20the%20enormous%20job%20companies%20have%20to%20not%20only%20encourage%20AI%20adoption%20but%20also%20equip%20employees%20with%20what%20they%20need%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20transformation%20that%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20positive%20story%20to%20be%20told%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jack%20Azagury%2C%20the%20group%20chief%20executive%20for%20consulting%20at%20Accenture.%20%26quot%3BRelated%20to%20that%20is%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20reskilling%20and%20training%20that's%20going%20to%20need%20to%20happen%20to%20make%20sure%20nobody's%20left%20behind%20on%20this%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20article%2C%20discover%20what%20each%20board%20member%20told%20us%20about%20their%20workplace%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E'We're%20trying%20to%20understand%20a%20more%20holistic%20view%20of%20worker%20well-being'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShane%20Koller%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20Ancestry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20topics%20we're%20most%20focused%20on%20are%20worker%20well-being%20and%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20transitioned%20to%20a%20hybrid-flexible%20work%20environment%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20trying%20to%20understand%20both%20the%20positives%20and%20the%20negatives%20from%20that%20shift.%20We've%20been%20a%20very%20culture-centric%20company%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20having%20more%20people%20distributed%20throughout%20the%20world%2C%20there's%20a%20question%20coming%20up%20more%20often%20about%20whether%20or%20not%20people%20feel%20too%20disconnected%20from%20their%20colleagues%2C%20so%20we're%20trying%20to%20understand%20a%20more%20holistic%20view%20of%20worker%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion.%20We%20are%20looking%20to%20build%20products%20that%20bring%20more%20people%20in%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20We%20believe%20our%20workforce%20needs%20to%20represent%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20world%20in%20order%20to%20build%20great%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20key%20to%20unlocking%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20employees%20are%20embracing%20it%20and%20are%20excited%20about%20the%20value'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucrecia%20Borgonovo%2C%20chief%20talent%20and%20organizational-effectiveness%20officer%2C%20Mastercard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20of%20mind%20is%20C-suite%20innovation%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20around%20organizational%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Mastercard%20announced%20changes%20in%20our%20organizational%20structure%20in%20support%20of%20the%20new%20vision%20and%20strategic%20priorities%20that%20our%20CEO%20has%20laid%20out%3A%20How%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20we're%20structuring%20to%20unlock%20the%20potential%20and%20growth%20of%20the%20organization%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERelated%20to%20that%20is%20AI.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20new%20organizational%20structure%2C%20we%20announced%20our%20chief%20AI%20and%20data%20officer%2C%20one%20individual%20who%20would%20help%20bring%20together%20a%20cohesive%20strategy%20and%20vision%20for%20the%20organization's%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20unlocking%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20employees%20are%20embracing%20it%20and%20are%20excited%20about%20the%20value%20these%20new%20technologies%20can%20have%20on%20their%20well-being%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20resources%20available%20for%20employees%2C%20whether%20they're%20on%20demand%20or%20self-paced%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20they%20are%20in%20their%20AI%20journey%20and%20the%20type%20of%20work%20that%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20C-suite%20transformation%20is%20pervasive'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJack%20Azagury%2C%20group%20chief%20executive%20for%20consulting%2C%20Accenture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20the%20work%20that%20I%20do%20with%20clients%2C%20the%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20C-suite%20transformation%20is%20pervasive.%20In%20over%20400%20client%20discussions%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20months%2C%20only%20three%20did%20not%20include%20the%20topic%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20our%20clients%20have%20dozens%20of%20AI%20pilots%20everywhere.%20Very%20few%20have%20a%20coherent%20business%20case%20and%20a%20true%20reinvention%20and%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20at%20that%20intersection%2C%20how%20do%20you%20take%20a%20few%20areas%20of%20the%20company%20and%20look%20at%20them%20end%20to%20end%20with%20a%20business%20case%20that%20could%20include%20revenue%20uplift%2C%20or%20cost%2C%20or%20employee%20engagement%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20real%20business%20case%20and%20a%20real%20talent%20strategy.%20How%20do%20you%20retrain%20your%20employees%20and%20reskill%3F%20What%20new%20jobs%20do%20you%20need%3F%20What%20jobs%20will%20go%20away%3F%20What%20superpowers%20will%20employees%20get%3F%20And%20then%20having%20the%20right%20tech%20stack%2C%20the%20right%20data%2C%20the%20right%20responsible%20AI%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20you%20have%20a%20holistic%20C-suite%20transformation%20powered%20by%20a%20move%20away%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20AI%20pilots%20that%20are%20just%20plugged%20into%20existing%20processes%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20interesting%20but%20not%20having%20a%20fundamental%20impact%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'C-suite%20transformation%20is%20harder%20and%20more%20interesting%20than%20ever'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlicia%20Pittman%2C%20global%20people-team%20chair%2C%20BCG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20responsible%20for%20driving%20generative-AI%20usage%20across%20BCG.%20We%20want%20our%20people%20to%20be%20at%20that%20cutting%20edge%20in%20terms%20of%20responsible%20AI%20and%20understanding%20all%20the%20risks%20of%20it%2C%20to%20use%20it%20creatively%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20live%20in%20our%20clients'%20shoes%20about%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20make%20this%20amazing%20technology%20have%20high%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20driving%20better%2C%20higher-quality%20impact%20and%20insights%20for%20us%2C%20which%20is%20most%20important.%20It%20is%20driving%20areas%20of%20productivity.%20But%20the%20other%20thing%20that%20lights%20me%20up%20the%20most%20is%20that%20it's%20really%20improving%20what%20I%20would%20call%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20quotes%20I%20love%20is%20from%20focus%20groups%20where%20someone%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20I%20love%20about%20AI%20is%20that%20it%20saves%20me%20at%20the%20ugliest%20hours%20of%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%20That%20time%20when%20you're%20sitting%20at%20a%20blank%20screen%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%20that's%20when%20AI%20really%20is%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC-suite%20transformation%20is%20harder%20and%20more%20interesting%20than%20ever.%20The%20markets%20are%20volatile.%20The%20half-life%20of%20market%20leadership%20keeps%20getting%20shorter%20and%20shorter.%20We%20have%20C-suite%20executives%20and%20the%20clients%20that%20we%20serve%20wrestling%20%E2%80%94%20needing%20to%20both%20save%20costs%20but%20also%20invest%20in%20AI%20and%20change%20the%20way%20they%20lead%20and%20manage%20their%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E'AI%20is%20not%20about%20cost%20takeout.%20It's%20about%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20more%20and%20amplify%20the%20potential%20of%20our%20employees.'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnant%20Adya%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%2C%20service-offering%20head%2C%20and%20head%20of%20Americas%20delivery%2C%20Infosys%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDEI%2C%20and%20within%20that%2C%20gender%20diversity%2C%20is%20something%20that%20we%20are%20very%20passionate%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20company%20level%2C%20we%20are%20at%2039.3%25%20women%2C%20but%20as%20you%20go%20up%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20the%20gender%20diversity%20actually%20drops.%20So%20we%20are%20deliberately%20trying%20to%20see%20what%20we%20can%20do%20to%20improve%20that%20percentage%20at%20senior%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20AI.%20And%20the%20way%20we%20look%20at%20AI%20is%20it's%20not%20about%20cost%20takeout%20or%20cost%20savings%2C%20but%20it%20is%20about%20how%20we%20use%20AI%20and%20amplify%20the%20potential%20of%20our%20employees%20to%20do%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20think%20that%20with%20AI%2C%20you%20can%20take%20cost%20out%2C%20you%20can%20save%20money.%20But%20AI%2C%20and%20especially%20generative%20AI%2C%20is%20not%20about%20cost%20takeout.%20It's%20about%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20more%20and%20amplify%20the%20potential%20of%20our%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Studies%20have%20shown%20that%20employees%20want%20managers%20who%20are%20engaged%2C%20who%20are%20coaches%20versus%20supervisors'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarjorie%20Powell%2C%20chief%20human-resource%20officer%20and%20senior%20vice%20president%2C%20AARP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topics%20we've%20been%20focusing%20on%20are%20workplace%20well-being%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20emerging%20tech.%20We%20have%20to%20reach%20our%2038%20million%20members%2C%20and%20now%20with%20the%20use%20of%20this%20technology%2C%20we%20can%20meet%20them%20where%20they%20are%20and%20personalize%20their%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20for%20us%20to%20do%20this%2C%20we're%20allowing%20our%20staff%20to%20use%20AI%20within%20their%20jobs%20and%20to%20create%20innovative%20ways%20to%20amplify%20their%20work%20and%20meet%20their%20goals%20and%20objectives.%20We've%20always%20been%20very%20excited%20about%20adopting%20technologies%2C%20particularly%20as%20it%20pertains%20to%20making%20people's%20lives%20better%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20worker%20well-being%20because%20of%20the%20new%20hybrid%20work%20environment%2C%20and%20this%20goes%20to%20our%20people-leader%20effectiveness.%20Studies%20have%20shown%20that%20employees%20want%20managers%20who%20are%20engaged%2C%20who%20are%20coaches%20versus%20supervisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20are%20transforming%20that%20leadership%20quotient%20for%20our%20people%20leaders%20within%20the%20company%20to%20be%20able%20to%20adjust%20to%20that%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20have%20a%20very%20robust%20work%20environment%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20the%20person%20sits%20or%20where%20they%20work%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E'We've%20had%20to%20move%20upstream%20from%20being%20focused%20on%20workplace%20to%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20work%20and%20the%20workforce%20itself'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeil%20Murray%2C%20CEO%2C%20Work%20Dynamics%20at%20JLL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day%20job%20is%20working%20with%20the%20biggest%20corporations%20in%20the%20world%20and%20helping%20them%20with%20their%20workplace%20strategy%2C%20which%20obviously%20has%20changed%20quite%20dramatically%20over%20the%20last%20number%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20to%20move%20upstream%20from%20being%20focused%20on%20workplace%20to%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20work%20and%20the%20workforce%20itself%2C%20hence%20worker%20well-being%20being%20at%20the%20center%20of%20what%20we%20do%20and%20our%20thinking.%20The%20second%20thing%20would%20be%20C-suite%20transformation.%20For%20me%2C%20that%20incorporates%20both%20AI%20and%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20on%20the%20executive%20board%20of%20a%20global%20Fortune%20200%20business%2C%20the%20world%20has%20changed%20quite%20dramatically%20for%20us%20in%20how%20we%20organize%20ourselves%20in%20terms%20of%20operating%20model.%20The%20skills%20required%20have%20changed%20quite%20dramatically.%20The%20notion%20of%20empathetic%20leaders%20who%20deeply%20understand%20people%20but%20also%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20leverage%20platforms%20at%20scale%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20ongoing%20geopolitical%20tensions%20and%20macro%20challenges%20that%20seem%20to%20have%20become%20the%20norm%20in%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20doesn't%20serve%20us%20well%20is%20the%20notion%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20nationalism%20and%20protectionism%20%E2%80%94%20how%20do%20we%20deal%20with%20that%3F%20How%20do%20we%20find%20the%20balance%20between%20global%20vertical%20expertise%20with%20the%20local%20knowledge%20and%20execution%20required%20to%20operate%20in%20this%20world%20around%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'We%20have%20made%20significant%20commitments%20to%20responsible%20AI'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaggie%20Hulce%2C%20chief%20revenue%20officer%2C%20Indeed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20three%20seconds%2C%20somebody%20gets%20a%20job%20on%20Indeed.%20We%20come%20at%20this%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20how%20we%20help%20our%20employees%20but%20also%20how%20we're%20helping%20the%20world%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20AI%2C%20we're%20thinking%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20to%20improve%20how%20we%20work%2C%20fraud%20detection%2C%20next%20best%20action%20marketing%20copy%2C%20many%20things%20like%20that.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20commitment%20to%20help%2030%20million%20people%20facing%20bias%20get%20hired.%20And%20so%20we%20have%20made%20significant%20commitments%20to%20responsible%20AI%20and%20have%20published%20our%20responsible-AI%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20focus%20for%20us%20is%20worker%20well-being.%20We%20have%20a%20work-happiness%20score%2C%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20dataset%20in%20the%20world%20of%20what%20makes%20workers%20happy%20in%20their%20roles.%20It%20includes%20lots%20of%20different%20dimensions%2C%20like%20fair%20pay%2C%20flexibility%2C%20inclusion%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20how%20your%20manager%20works%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20to%20use%20this%20dataset%20to%20help%20advocate%20for%20better%20work%20for%20people%2C%20given%20research%20that%20shows%20many%20people%20don't%20love%20their%20jobs%20and%20are%20not%20totally%20thriving%20at%20work.%20We%20also%20study%20it%20for%20ourselves%2C%20and%20there%20are%20things%20we're%20working%20on%20ourselves%20as%20an%20employer%20to%20make%20our%20workplace%20a%20place%20where%20people%20want%20to%20stay%20and%20grow%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E'There's%20a%20constant%20discussion%20around%20not%20only%20whether%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20replace%20my%20role%20but%20also%20how%20to%20stay%20relevant'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKenon%20Chen%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20strategy%20and%20growth%2C%20Clear%20Capital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20the%20property-appraisal%20industry%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20from%20an%20equity%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20seen%20ourselves%20as%20a%20company%20that%20wants%20to%20bring%20accuracy%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20modernization%20to%20the%20process%20of%20valuing%20properties.%20That's%20why%20AI%20is%20an%20important%20topic%20for%20us%20because%20it's%20not%20so%20much%20about%20just%20creating%20efficiencies%3B%20it's%20about%20creating%20more%20accurate%20outcomes%20and%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20a%20really%20strong%20tie%20between%20AI%20and%20worker%20well-being%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20solutions%20that%20AI%20could%20be%20appropriate%20for%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20way%20that%20people%20work%20and%20how%20their%20jobs%20might%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20work%20directly%20with%20real-estate%20professionals%20%E2%80%94%20appraisers%2C%20real-estate%20brokers%2C%20and%20agents%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20constant%20discussion%20around%20not%20only%20whether%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20replace%20my%20role%20but%20also%2