20least%20broadly.%20In%20the%20section%20entitled%20%26quot%3BCulture%2C%26quot%3B%20six%20of%20ten%20articles%20have%20to%20do%20with%20either%20marriage%2C%20child-rearing%2C%20or%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20piece%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20marriage%2C%20Helen%20M.%20Alvar%C3%A9%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20George%20Mason%20University's%20law%20school%2C%20blames%20%26quot%3Bcohabitation%2C%20premarital%20sexual%20relations%2C%20premarital%20childbearing%2C%20and%20pornography%26quot%3B%20for%20rising%20divorce%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPornography%20is%20also%20increasingly%20associated%20with%20relationship%20troubles%2C%20including%20greater%20divorce%20risks%20%E2%80%94%20interestingly%2C%20especially%20if%20married%20women%20watch%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlvar%C3%A9%20also%20regrets%20that%20Americans%20have%20more%20premarital%20sexual%20partners%20now%20than%20in%20earlier%20decades%20and%20argues%20that%20%26quot%3Bserial%20premarital%20sexual%20partnerships%20also%20undermine%20the%20opportunity%20for%20lifelong%20marriage.%26quot%3B%20Marrying%20later%20is%20also%20harmful%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20her%2C%20the%20risks%20accumulate%20for%20those%20who%20tie%20the%20knot%20after%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20is%20facing%20particular%20scrutiny%20for%20his%20comments%20on%20fertility.%20After%20his%20%26quot%3Bchildless%20cat%20ladies%26quot%3B%20quip%20went%20viral%2C%20other%20instances%2C%20like%20when%20he%20called%20Democrats%20without%20kids%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-vice-president-democratic-leaders-childless-sociopaths-2021-email-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bchildless%20sociopaths%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20gaining%20traction%20and%20hurting%20his%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-lowest-vice-president-approval-rating-republican-convention-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabysmal%20polling%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jennifer%20Lahl%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Bioethics%20and%20Culture%20Network%2C%20writes%20about%20that%20very%20issue%20in%20her%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELahl%20attributes%20declining%20fertility%20in%20part%20to%20later%20marriage%20and%20pregnancy%2C%20which%20is%20itself%20linked%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20women%20have%20been%20pursuing%20higher%20education%20and%20graduate%20degrees%20and%20spending%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20their%20most%20fertile%20years%20building%20their%20careers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20celebrities%20have%20children%20past%20the%20age%20of%2040%20and%20companies%20include%20benefits%20like%20egg%20freezing%2C%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20are%20lured%20into%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20can%20have%20children%20whenever%20they%20are%20finally%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20Lahl%20continues.%20She%20calls%20egg%20freezing%20a%20%26quot%3Bscheme%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20that%20women%20who%20are%20surrogates%20%26quot%3Bare%20exploited%20for%20their%20healthy%20reproductive%20capacities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20articles%20lament%20porn%20and%20premarital%20sex%2C%20such%20as%20one%20that%20argues%20we%20must%20publicly%20end%20the%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20revolution%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3Ba%20flourishing%20civil%20society%20is%20one%20built%20on%20strong%20marriages%20and%20happy%20families%20and%20that%20those%20in%20turn%20are%20built%20on%20personal%20virtue%20and%20an%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20sexual%20integrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20piece%20entitled%20%26quot%3BMom%20and%20Dad%3A%20Better%20Opportunity%20Together%26quot%3B%20calls%20the%20rising%20rate%20of%20%26quot%3Bunwed%20births%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3Btragedy%26quot%3B%20and%20argues%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ideal%20situation%20for%20any%20child%20is%20growing%20up%20with%20the%20mother%20and%20father%20who%20brought%20that%20child%20into%20this%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20deals%20with%20economic%20questions%2C%20particularly%20welfare.%20Writing%20about%20how%20the%20welfare%20state%20runs%20counter%20to%20his%20understanding%20of%20human%20nature%2C%20the%20columnist%20Cal%20Thomas%20calls%20welfare%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20poison%20that%20has%20produced%20an%20entitlement%20mentality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance's%20ties%20to%20the%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20which%20is%20the%20group%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-project-2025-conservative-political-playbook-heritage-foundation-trump-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProject%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20run%20deep%20%E2%80%94%20deeper%20than%20his%20roots%20as%20a%20politician.%20His%20introduction%20in%20the%202017%20report%20represents%20one%20of%20his%20earliest%20instances%20of%20public%20support%20for%20socially%20conservative%20values%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F03%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fvance-heritage-report.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-2025-heritage-foundation-donald-trump-elected-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparate%20himself%20from%20Project%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Democrats%20have%20latched%20onto%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-opening-argument-vote-for-me-decimate-project-2025-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecampaign%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20recently%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20make%20IVF%20free%20for%20all%20Americans%2C%20though%20provided%20no%20details%20on%20how%20the%20expensive%20proposal%20would%20work.%20Vance%20is%20having%20an%20even%20harder%20time%20creating%20daylight%20between%20himself%20and%20the%20organization.%20The%20senator%20is%20not%20embracing%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%202017%20volume%20wholeheartedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSenator%20Vance%20has%20long%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20supports%20I.V.F.%20and%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20every%20opinion%20in%20this%20seven-year-old%20report%2C%20which%20features%20a%20range%20of%20unique%20views%20from%20dozens%20of%20conservative%20thinkers%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20spokesperson%20Luke%20Schroeder%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20repeating%20the%20statement%20he%20gave%20to%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Heritage%20Foundation%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Times%20that%20Vance%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20%26quot%3Bproducing%20or%20approving%20the%20contents%20of%20the%202017%20Index%20of%20Culture%20and%20Opportunity.%26quot%3B%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20report%20likely%20won't%20make%20it%20any%20easier%20for%20the%20vice%20presidential%20hopeful%20to%20shake%20the%20electorate's%20focus%20on%20familial%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-heritage-foundation-project-2025-report-ivf-pornography-aboriton-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725388453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d74feb14a5cd1fcc8cc808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-heritage-foundation-project-2025-report-ivf-pornography-aboriton-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JD%20Vance%20called%20a%202017%20report%20from%20the%20Heritage%20Foundation%20that%20laments%20premarital%20sex%2C%20warns%20of%20IVF%2C%20and%20focuses%20on%20fertility%20rates%20%26quot%3Badmirable.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A161%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-heritage-foundatio