rs-begin-2010-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoar's%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20ongoing%20listeria%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoar's%20Head's%20%26quot%3Bnegligence%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20and%20distribution%20of%20%26quot%3Bdefective%20and%20unreasonably%20dangerous%26quot%3B%20lunch%20meats%20led%20to%20the%20July%2018%20death%20of%2088-year-old%20Virginia%20resident%20G%C3%BCnter%20Morgenstein%2C%20the%20man's%20family%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Boar's%20Head%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgenstein%2C%20a%20married%20father%2C%20purchased%20Boar's%20Head%20liverwurst%20and%20other%20Boar's%20Head%20products%20on%20June%2030%2C%20eating%20the%20deli%20meats%20on%20sandwiches%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20his%20family%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20filed%20last%20week%20in%20a%20Florida%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20subsequently%20became%20ill%2C%20suffering%20from%20weakness%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20fatigue%2C%20and%20a%20fever%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20adding%20that%20Morgenstein's%20condition%20worsened%20and%20he%20was%20hospitalized%20on%20July%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20blood%20culture%20came%20back%20positive%20for%20listeria%20bacteria%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgenstein%20%26quot%3Bingested%20listeria%20from%20the%20product%20and%20developed%20listeriosis%2C%20encephalitis%2C%20meningitis%2C%20sepsis%2C%20and%20sustained%20other%20injuries%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20ingestion%20of%20the%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20died%20after%20spending%2010%20days%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Morgenstein%20was%20a%20Holocaust%20survivor%2C%20who%20according%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailypress.com%2Fobituaries%2Fgnter-g-morgenstein%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobituary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20left%20East%20Berlin%20%26quot%3Bwith%20just%20the%20clothes%20on%20his%20back%26quot%3B%20in%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHealth%20officials%20later%20determined%20that%20Morgenstein%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bconfirmed%20case%20in%20the%20Boar's%20Head%20Listeria%20Outbreak%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20wrongful-death%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deli%20meat%20that%20Morgenstein%20consumed%20%26quot%3Bwas%20defective%20because%20it%20contained%20listeria%20and%20Defendant%20failed%20to%20give%20adequate%20warnings%20of%20the%20product's%20dangers%20that%20were%20known%20or%20by%20the%20application%20of%20reasonably%20developed%20human%20skill%20and%20foresight%20should%20have%20been%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20Simon%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Morgenstein's%20family%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20Morgenstein%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20have%20died%20from%20eating%20a%20sandwich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20this%20lawsuit%20and%20others%2C%20we%20will%20make%20sure%20that%20all%20listeria%20victims%20are%20fairly%20compensated%20for%20their%20losses%2C%20we%20will%20find%20out%20exactly%20how%20this%20happened%2C%20and%20we%20will%20force%20Boar's%20Head%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20never%20happens%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Simon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgenstein's%20son%2C%20Garshon%20Morgenstein%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20his%20family%20is%20%26quot%3Bdevastated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20that%20through%20the%20legal%20process%20we%20can%20make%20Boar's%20Head%20and%20other%20lunch%20meat%20products%20safer%20for%20future%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20son%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20information%20from%20the%20US%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%2057%20people%20have%20been%20hospitalized%20and%20at%20least%20nine%20people%20have%20died%20across%20the%20country%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Boar's%20Head%20deli%20meat%20listeria%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20largest%20listeriosis%20outbreak%20since%20the%202011%20outbreak%20linked%20to%20cantaloupe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CDC%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoar's%20Head%20has%20recalled%20millions%20of%20pounds%20of%20deli%20meats%20due%20to%20the%20outbreak%20and%20paused%20production%20at%20its%20Jarratt%2C%20Virginia%2C%20processing%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20product%20recall%20is%20limited%20to%20only%20our%20Jarratt%2C%20Virginia%20facility.%20And%2C%20only%20Boar's%20Head%20Liverwurst%20has%20been%20found%20to%20be%20adulterated%20with%20Listeria%20monocytogenes%2C%26quot%3B%20Boar's%20Head%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboarshead.com%2Fproducts-recall-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20updated%20statement%20posted%20on%20August%2029%2C%20the%20deli%20meat%20company%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20deeply%20regret%20the%20impact%20this%20recall%20has%20had%20on%20affected%20families.%20No%20words%20can%20fully%20express%20our%20sympathies%20and%20the%20sincere%20and%20deep%20hurt%20we%20feel%20for%20those%20who%20have%20suffered%20losses%20or%20endured%20illness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20conducting%20an%20extensive%20investigation%2C%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20USDA%20and%20government%20regulatory%20agencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20industry's%20leading%20food%20safety%20experts%2C%20to%20determine%20how%20our%20liverwurst%20produced%20at%20our%20Jarratt%2C%20Virginia%20facility%20was%20adulterated%20and%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20happening%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fboars-head-listeria-recall-fcde06b66dca38d53361c92495a7cfed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewly%20released%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20th