0and%20our%20sympathies%20remain%20with%20the%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216d45694-72d3-4311-8ba3-d82a529dec18%5C%22%3EA%20deadly%20crash%2C%20and%20alleged%20mistakes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2020%2C%202023%2C%20Rushfeldt%20and%20Maclean%20were%20enlisted%20to%20fly%20the%20plane%20from%20Santa%20Rosa%2C%20California%20to%20Honolulu%2C%20with%20an%20ultimate%20destination%20of%20Fiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20outfitted%20with%20a%20fuel%20bladder%20designed%20to%20extend%20its%20range%20but%20the%20equipment%20malfunctioned%20and%20it%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20around%2030%20miles%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20California%2C%20according%20to%20the%20court%20filings.%20The%20plane%20crashed%20into%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20and%20Rushfeldt%20and%20Maclean%20were%20found%20dead%20inside%2C%20but%20their%20bodies%20could%20not%20be%20recovered%20before%20the%20plane%20sank%2C%20the%20lawsuits%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERushfeldt's%20family%20alleged%20in%20their%20complaint%20that%20Bayshore%20Global%20and%20a%20related%20corporate%20entity%20Seafly%20made%20numerous%20errors%20in%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20aircraft.%20The%20fuel%20bladder%20equipment%20was%20wrongly%20installed%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20memory%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20by%20following%20a%20checklist%2C%20proper%20logs%20of%20the%20alterations%20were%20not%20recorded%2C%20and%20the%20correct%20certificates%20were%20not%20obtained%2C%20the%20legal%20documents%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20lawsuit%20from%20July%20also%20charges%20Brin%20and%20his%20family%20office%20of%20tortious%20interference%20with%20a%20dead%20body%2C%20alleging%20that%20his%20team%20promised%20to%20recover%20Rushfeldt's%20body%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20secretly%20plotting%20never%20to%20do%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e99d45b-088b-480d-8b82-10dd76dcb4dd%5C%22%3EBrin's%20lawyers%20tried%20to%20dismiss%20earlier%20suit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in