EThe%20study%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Impacts%20of%20Layoffs%20Announcement%20on%20Cybersecurity%20Breaches%2C%26quot%3B%20explores%20the%20behaviors%20of%20people%20affected%20by%20job%20cuts%2C%20including%20whether%20they%20seek%20to%20%26quot%3Bpunish%26quot%3B%20what%20they%20consider%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20business%26quot%3B%20by%20hacking%2C%20said%20Thi%20Tran%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20management%20information%20systems%20at%20Binghamton%20University%20who%20led%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thi%20Tran%20sitting%20in%20a%20chair%20and%20holding%20a%20phone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d2067843b5e59d16b727e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThi%20Tran%20is%20an%20IT%20expert%20who%20specializes%20in%20cybersecurity%20research.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Binghamton%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETran%2C%20who%20presented%20the%20study%20at%20the%20Pacific%20Asia%20Conference%20on%20Information%20Systems%20in%20Vietnam%20in%20July%2C%20said%20the%20research%20was%20inspired%20by%20news%20of%20companies%20across%20industries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-us-these-are-companies-making-cuts-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20how%20terrible%20it%20is%2C%20that%20layoffs%20can%20cause%20anger%20and%20potentially%20ruin%20people's%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20know%20how%20dangerous%20it%20is%20when%20people%20get%20pissed%20off%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETran%20discussed%20what%20companies%20should%20know%20about%20the%20connection%20between%20layoffs%20and%20cybersecurity%20breaches%20and%20how%20organizations%20can%20minimize%20their%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20layoffs%20put%20companies%20at%20risk%20of%20cyberattacks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20might%20think%20that%20hackers%20are%20empowered%20when%20they%20have%20technical%20abilities%2C%20but%20in%20most%20cases%20it's%20that%20they%20get%20triggered%20and%20have%20some%20motivation.%20Getting%20laid%20off%20can%20trigger%20that%20revenge%2C%20and%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20perform%20an%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20research%20suggests%20that%20the%20consequence%20of%20a%20layoff%20announcement%20is%20the%20likelihood%20of%20getting%20attacked%20and%20that%20the%20severity%20will%20be%20higher%20because%20hackers%20try%20to%20create%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20threats%2C%20such%20as%20ex-employees%2C%20are%20the%20biggest%20threat%20because%20they%20know%20about%20all%20the%20systems%2C%20layers%20of%20protection%2C%20and%20policies.%20So%20they%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20harmful%20things%20to%20the%20company%20when%20motivated%20by%20layoffs.%20Imagine%20that%20the%20laid-off%20employee%20worked%20for%20the%20IT%20department%20or%20the%20security%20department%3A%20They%20know%20about%20every%20single%20corner%20and%20how%20to%20bypass%20all%20the%20protection%20layers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20companies%20protect%20themselves%20when%20announcing%20layoffs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20terminate%20laid-off%20employees'%20access%20to%20systems%20shortly%20after%20notifying%20them%3B%20announcing%20layoffs%20too%20far%20in%20advance%20and%20then%20terminating%20access%20later%20can%20open%20the%20door%20to%20cybersecurity%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20companies%20need%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20employees%20to%20minimize%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20layoff%20and%20explain%20why%20access%20has%20been%20terminated.%20Something%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20unfortunate%20situation.%20We%20know%20this%20is%20very%20hard%20for%20you%2C%20but%20this%20is%20what%20we%20have%20to%20do%20for%20the%20entire%20company.%26quot%3B%20Remind%20people%20of%20their%20connection%20to%20the%20company%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20data%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrepare%20for%20the%20worst-case%20scenario.%20Think%20about%20the%20potential%20losses%20and%20costs%20of%20a%20breach%20and%20how%20you%20can%20strengthen%20security%20layers%2C%20such%20as%20with%20antivirus%20software%2C%20intrusion-detection%20systems%2C%20firewalls%2C%20and%20warnings%20about%20suspicious%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20you%20would%20know%20beforehand%20that%20there's%20something%20wrong%20with%20the%20system%2C%20and%20the%20sooner%20you%20know%2C%20the%20more%20you%20can%20minimize%20harm.%20But%20you%20can't%20eliminate%20100%25%20of%20possible%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20role%20does%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20play%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayoff%20announcements%20can%20bring%20negative%20publicity.%20They%20could%20send%20a%20message%20that%20your%20company%20is%20doing%20something%20harmful%20to%20the%20public%20or%20experiencing%20financial%20problems%20or%20poor%20leadership.%20This%20could%20make%20someone%20want%20to%20hack%20your%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20minimize%20attacks%2C%20improve%20and%20emphasize%20your%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%2C%20which%20is%20the%20company's%20reputation%20and%20image%2C%20and%20demonstrate%20the%20company's%20commitment%20to%20social%20and%20environmental%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20proactive%20and%20emphasizing%20ethical%20conduct%20and%20data%20security%20during%20layoffs%20could%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20data%20breaches%20in%20those%20situations.%20It%20will%20enhance%20trust%20with%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20aspect%20of%20layoffs%20and%20data%20breaches%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20study%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20to%20collect%20publicly%20available%20records%20showing%20the%20dates%20of%20a%20layoff%20announcement%20and%20the%20dates%20that%20a%20breach%20happened.%20We'll%20try%20to%20see%20if%20there%20is%20any%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20survey%20people%20about%20their%20ability%20and%20technical%20skills%20to%20formulate%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20company%20and%20how%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20influences%20that%20decision.%20We%20want%20to%20capture%20online%20and%20social-media%20conversations%20to%20tabulate%20positive%20and%20negative%20emotions%20about%20a%20company%20after%20announcing%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20things%20we%20want%20to%20explore%20that%20we%20hope%20can%20help%20guide%20policies%20for%20how%20companies%20can%20prepare%20for%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20and%20minimize%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20data%20breach%20after%20layoffs%20are%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-can-respond-to-cybersecurity-risks-after-layoffs-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725384022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d719521d8d2deb96b819c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-can-respond-to-cybersecurity-risks-after-layoffs-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20study%20suggests%20layoffs%20can%20lead%20to%20cyberattacks%20by%20ex-employees.%20Here's%20how%20companies%20can%20thwart%20hackers%20and%20avoid%20data%20breaches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erica%20Sweeney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-can-respond-to-cybersecurity-