ection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-election-congress-aap-rahul-gandhi-urges-party-to-consider-alliance-in-haryana-what-aap-says-6480753%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20Urges%20Congress%20To%20Consider%20AAP%20Deal%20In%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wanted%20to%20retain%20the%20alliance%20to%20guard%20against%20division%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Haryana%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20contested%20the%20state's%2010%20seats%209%3A1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%20five%20from%20its%20share.%20The%20AAP%20lost%20the%20one%20seat%20it%20was%20contesting%20-%20Kurukshetra%20-%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Naveen%20Jindal%20by%20around%2029%2C000%20votes.%20The%20two%20parties%20got%2021.19%20per%20cent%20and%201.11%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20Combined%2C%20this%20was%20well%20below%20the%2036.5%20per%20cent%20amassed%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20Congress'%20vote%20share%20was%20lower%20than%20it%20managed%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20(in%20which%20the%20BJP%20got%20over%2058%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes)%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20(the%20BJP%20got%2036.49%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20consolidation%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20voter%20bases%20was%20seen%20as%20helping%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20win%20its%20five%20seats%20and%20stop%20the%20BJP%20from%20a%20second%20straight%20clean%20sweep%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similarly%20united%20showing%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20believes%2C%20is%20needed%20to%20vote%20out%20the%20state's%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20continue%20momentum%20generated%20by%20the%20party%20and%20INDIA