V%20Tuesday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andhra%20Doctors%20Remove%2024-Week-Old%20'Stone%20Baby'%20From%20Woman's%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20the%20King%20George%20Hospital%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Visakhapatnam%20successfully%20removed%20the%20calcified%20remains%20of%20a%2024-week-old%20fetus%20from%20a%20patient's%20abdominal%20cavity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20condition%20known%20as%20a%20'stone%20baby'%20or%20%26quot%3Blithopedion%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20a%20rare%20phenomenon%20which%20occurs%20most%20commonly%20when%20a%20fetus%20dies%20during%20an%20abdominal%20pregnancy%2C%20is%20too%20large%20to%20be%20reabsorbed%20by%20the%20body%2C%20and%20subsequently%20becomes%20calcified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELithopedia%20may%20occur%20from%2014%20weeks%20gestation%20to%20full%20term.%20It%20is%20not%20unusual%20for%20a%20stone%20baby%20to%20remain%20undiagnosed%20for%20decades%20and%20to%20be%20found%20well%20after%20natural%20menopause%3B%20diagnosis%20often%20happens%20when%20the%20patient%20is%20examined%20for%20other%20conditions%20that%20require%20being%20subjected%20to%20an%20X-ray%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2027-year-old%20patient%20from%20the%20Anakapalle%20district%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20arrived%20at%20KGH%20in%20the%20third%20week%20of%20August%2C%20suffering%20from%20severe%20abdominal%20pain.%20The%20baby's%20rib%20cage%2C%20skull%2C%20pelvic%20bone%2C%20scapula%2C%20etc.%20were%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vani%2C%20Professor%20of%20Obstetrics%20at%20KGH%20conducted%20an%20MRI%20scan%2C%20which%20showed%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20calcified%20mass%20resembling%20a%20%26quot%3Bnest%20of%20bones%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20abdomen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20team%20performed%20surgery%20on%20August%2031.%20The%20operation%20was%20successful%2C%20and%20the%20woman%20is%20recovering%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fspeaking-of-science%2Fwp%2F2015%2F08%2F05%2Fhow-one-woman-carried-a-stone-fetus-inside-her-for-over-60-years%2F%5C%22%3EIn%202015%2C%20a%2091-year-old%20woman%20in%20Chile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Estela%20Melendez%2C%20did%20not%20know%20that%20a%20calcified%20fetus%20had%20been%20in%20her%20uterus%20for%20over%2060%20years%20until%20the%20doctors%20spotted%20something%20on%20her%20X-ray%20when%20she%20suffered%20a%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20had%20a%20lump%20for%20over%2060%20years%20but%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20situation.%20The%20calcified%20fetus%20did%20not%20pose%20any%20risk%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725380820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fdoctor-generic_650x400_81520610288.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fandhra-doctors-remove-24-week-old-stone-baby-from-womans-body-6483601%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20at%20the%20King%20George%20Hospital%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Visakhapatnam%20successfully%20removed%20the%20calcified%20remains%20of%20a%2024-week-old%20fetus%20from%20a%20patient's%20abdominal%20cavity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fandhra-doctors-remove-24-week-old-stone-baby-from-womans-body-6483601%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20aide%20to%20New%20York's%20guv%2C%20husband%20arrested%3A%20'Undisclosed%20agent%20of%20China%20govt'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725380725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113035974%2Cimgsize-1200702.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fformer-aide-to-new-yorks-guv-husband-arrested-undisclosed-agent-of-china-govt%2Farticleshow%2F113035932.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%