13035017.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDirector%20Amar%20Kaushik%E2%80%99s%20Stree%202%20has%20become%20the%20biggest%20Hindi%20release%20of%202024%2C%20smashing%20records%20with%20over%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%20global%20earnings.%20While%20the%20film%20continues%20to%20break%20records%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20reported%20PR%20game%20has%20shifted%20the%20focus%20towards%20the%20rivalry%20between%20Shraddha%20Kapoor%20and%20Rajkummar%20Rao%20over%20who%20deserves%20more%20credit%20for%20the%20film's%20success.%20Kaushik%20recently%20addressed%20this%20controversy%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20bond%20among%20the%20cast%20remains%20intact%20despite%20the%20noise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fstree-2-director-amar-kaushik-denies-credit-war-between-shraddha-kapoor-and-rajkummar-rao-caused-any-rift-within-the-team-its-my-film%2Farticleshow%2F113035017.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explainer%3A%20How%20Pilots%20Eject%20From%20An%20Unrecoverable%20MiG-29%20Jet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20MiG-29%20fighter%20jet%20crashed%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Barmer%20yesterday%20during%20a%20routine%20night%20training%20sortie.%20The%20pilot%20ejected%20safely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20said%20the%20MiG-29%20fighter%20jet%20faced%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20snag%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20night%20sortie%2C%20and%20a%20court%20of%20inquiry%20has%20been%20ordered.%20There%20was%20no%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20property.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmig-29-fighter-jet-crashes-in-rajasthan-pilot-safe-6476114%5C%22%3EThe%20pilot%20crashed%20the%20jet%20away%20from%20a%20residential%20area%20%3C%2Fa%3Earound%2010%20pm%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiG-29%2C%20NATO%20name%20'Fulcrum'%20and%20Indian%20name%20'Baaz'%2C%20is%20an%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20jet%20originating%20in%20Soviet%20Russia.%20It%20was%20formally%20inducted%20into%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20in%201987%2C%20initially%20with%20two%20squadrons%20-%20No.%2028%20and%20No.%2047%20Squadrons.%20The%20MiG-29K%20fighter%20jets%20deployed%20on%20the%20Navy's%20aircraft%20carriers%20are%20currently%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20Navy's%20fighter%20operations.%20They%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20the%20Tejas%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20pilots%20eject%20from%20a%20fighter%20jet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zvezda%20K-36D%20zero-zero%20ejection%20seat%20is%20onboard%20the%20MiG-29%20fighter%20jet.%20It%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20ejection%20seats%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20also%20deployed%20on%20Air%20Force%20Su-30MKI%20fighter%20jets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fren0m8c8_fighter-jet-mig29-crashes_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20of%20the%20MiG-29%20fighter%20jet%20ejected%20safely%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Barmer%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20are%20designed%20to%20eject%20pilots%20from%20zero%20position%2C%20i.e.%20stationary%20position%20to%20a%20considerable%20height%20to%20deploy%20parachutes.%20Zero%20position%20refers%20to%20zero%20altitude%20or%20zero%20speed.%C2%A0The%20development%20of%20Martin-Baker%20zero-zero%20ejection%20seats%20by%20the%20British%20(the%20West)%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20development%20of%20zero-zero%20seats%20by%20the%20Soviets.%20The%20Tejas%20fighter%20jet%20has%20the%20Matin-Baker%20zero-zero%20ejection%20seat%20deployed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20zero-zero%20capability%20was%20developed%20to%20help%20pilots%20escape%20unrecoverable%20situations%20during%20low-altitude%20or%20low-speed%20flights%20and%20ground%20mishaps%20during%20takeoff%20or%20landing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ejection%20seat%20is%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20'Egress'%20system%2C%20which%20means%20the%20%26quot%3Bway%20to%20exit%26quot%3B.%20The%20system%20includes%20explosives%20under%20the%20seat%2C%20the%20canopy%2C%20and%20parachutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pilot%20pulls%20the%20ejection%20handles%20(in%20the%20case%20of%20K-36D%2C%20they%20are%20located%20in%20the%20front%20of%20the%20ejection%20seat)%2C%20the%20canopy%20of%20the%20aircraft%20is%20jettisoned.%20The%20explosive%20cartridge%20catapults%20the%20seat%20along%20the%20guide%20rails%2C%20and%20a%20leg-restrain%20system%20is%20activated.%20It%20protects%20the%20pilot's%20legs%20from%20getting%20caught%20during%20the%20ejection.%20The%20rocket%20propels%20the%20pilot%20to%20a%20considerable%20height%2C%20at%20least%20300-400%20feet%20so%20that%20ejecting%20pilot%20avoids%20the%20tail%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20which%20is%20rapidly%20descending.%20When%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20pilot%20are%20separated%2C%20the%20harness%20and%20the%20pilot%20are%20released%20from%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20parachute%20deployment%20signal%20is%20activated%20which%20automatically%20opens%20the%20chute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20angle%20of%20ejection%20is%20crucial.%20The%20fighter%20jet%20moves%20forward%20and%20the%20line%20of%20ejection%20is%20perpendicular%20to%20it%20to%20move%20the%20pilot%20away%20from%20the%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20exit%20process%20occurs%20in%20less%20than%2010-15%20seconds%20-%20From%20the%20pulling%20of%20ejection%20handles%20to%20the%20deployment%20of%20parachutes.%20The%20pilot%20in%20yesterday's%20crash%20would%20have%20experienced%20high-G%20forces%20during%20ejection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20K-36D%20Caught%20The%20World's%20Attention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force%20Materiel%20Command%20at%20the%20Wright-Patterson%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Ohio%20conducted%20a%20comparative%20testing%20study%20to%20understand%20the%20components%20of%20the%20K-36D%20ejection%20seat%20with%20its%20US%20counterpart.%20The%20interim%20report%20published%20in%201993%20and%201994%20%C2%A0gave%20an%20in-depth%20analysis%20of%20the%20K-36D%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-36D%20ejection%20seat%20gained%20wide%20attention%20at%20the%201989%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20when%20the%20pilot%20successfully%20ejected%20from%20a%20MiG-29%20from%20an%20extremely%20low-altitude%20engine%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20has%20been%20a%20standard%20of%20Russian%20high-performance%20aircraft%2C%20and%20the%20seats%20have%20an%20impeccable%20record%20of%20survivable%20ejection%20from%20speeds%20of%200%20to%20755%20Knots%20of%20Equivalent%20Air%20Speed%20(KEAS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Foh3c3U5ajWE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Mig%2029%20Airshow%20Crash%201989%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20the%20pilot%20ejected%20from%20the%20jet%20after%20an%20engine%20failure%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20300%20feet%2C%20with%20an%2080-degree%20pitch-down%20altitude%2C%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20aircraft%20was%20100%20knots%20(185%20km%2Fhr).%20The%20pilot%20ejected%2C%20and%20the%20parachutes%20were%20deployed%20just%2015%20ft%20above%20the%20ground.%20He%20survived%20and%20suffered%20minor%20injuries.%20The%20incident%20caught%20the%20US'%20attention%20and%20it%20later%20analysed%20the%20K-36D%20ejection%20system%20in%20detail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20The%20Ejection%20Seat%20System%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-36D%20ejection%20seat%20is%20designed%20by%20the%20Zvezda%20Design%20Bureau%20in%20Russia.%20It%20is%20said%20to%20be%20strong%20with%20the%20integration%20of%20ejection%20seat%20subsystems%20such%20as%20windblast%20protection%2C%20leg%20and%20arm%20restraints%2C%20leg%20lifters%2C%20and%20a%20vented%20helmet%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20interface%20with%20the%20seat%20headrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-36D%20and%20the%20flight%20equipment%2C%20such%20as%20the%20pressure%20suit%20and%20helmet%2C%20were%20designed%20together%20as%20a%20single%20system%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F05gv2ss_k36d-ejection-seat_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20is%20incorporated%20with%20telescoping%20stabilization%20booms%2C%20which%20ensure%20aerodynamic%20stability.%20The%20other%20subsystems%20that%20have%20been%20integrated%20into%20the%20total%20design%20seat%20include%20the%20windblast%20deflector%2C%20rocket%20propulsion%20system%2C%20crew%20recovery%20parachutes%2C%20restraint%20devices%20and%20sequencing%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-36D%20ejection%20system%20is%20advertised%20by%20the%20Russians%20as%20an%20advanced%20ejection%20seat%2C%20providing%20survival%20of%20the%20pilot%20up%20to%20Mach%203%20speed%20and%2080%2C000%20feet%20altitude.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fr9d1nvv_k36d-ejection-seat_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stabilization%20booms%20in%20K-36D%20play%20an%20essential%20role%20in%20providing%20safety%20for%20the%20pilot.%20In%20yesterday's%20ejection%2C%20the%20telescoping%20stabilization%20booms%2C%20installed%20at%20an%20angle%20of%2015%20degrees%20from%20the%20seat%20flight%2C%20extended%20pressure%20to%20assist%20in%20keeping%20the%20seat%20stable%20from%20the%20time%20it%20separated%20from%20the%20aircraft%20until%20parachute%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Credit%3A%20K-36D%20EJECTION%20SEAT%20FOREIGN%20COMPARATIVE%20TESTING%20(FCT)%20PROGRAM%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Credit%3A%20K-36D%20EJECTION%20SEAT%20FOREIGN%20COMPARATIVE%20TESTING%20(FCT)%20PROGRAM%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Frka9b7t8_k36-ejection_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%3A%20K-36D%20EJECTION%20SEAT%20FOREIGN%20COMPARATIVE%20TESTING%20(FCT)%20PROGRAM%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20key%20components%20are%20leg%20lifters%2C%20leg%20restraints%2C%20and%20windblast%20deflectors%20-%20Additional%20protection%20against%20the%20aerodynamic%20forces%20experienced%20during%20ejection%2C%20restraint%20systems%2C%20helmet%20and%20headrest%20and%20arm%20paddles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-36D%20receives%20its%20parachute%20deployment%20signal%20from%20the%20aircraft%20airspeed%20and%20two%20onboard%20altitude%20pressure%2Ftiming%20devices.%20The%20parachute%20inflates%20automatically%20after%20seat%20and%20crewmember%20separation.%20The%20survival%20kit%20remains%20attached%20to%20the%20crewmember%20during%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20results%20conducted%20by%20the%20US%20concurred%20that%20the%20K-36%20ejection%20system%20provides%20superior-high-quality%20stability%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20team%20that%20has%20developed%20the%20K-36D%20has%20a%20solid%20understanding%20of%20the%20scientific%20principles%20behind%20the%20system's%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725378480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%