Cp%3EThe%20new%20Chancery%20of%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Brunei%20was%20launched%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20a%20rousing%20welcome%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20community.%20The%20new%20facility%2C%20which%20has%20come%20up%20at%20the%20Jalan%20Duta%20Diplomatic%20Enclave%2C%20is%20adjacent%20to%20the%20US%20Embassy%20in%20Bandar%20Seri%20Begawan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20(NSA)%20Ajit%20Doval%20were%20present%20on%20the%20occasion%20as%20the%20PM%20lit%20a%20lamp%20and%20unveiled%20a%20plaque%20at%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20launch%2C%20The%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20chancery%20complex%20embodies%20a%20profound%20sense%20of%20Indianness%2C%20masterfully%20integrating%20traditional%20motifs%20and%20lush%20tree%20plantations.%20The%20use%20of%20elegant%20claddings%20and%20durable%20Kota%20stones%20further%20enhances%20its%20aesthetic%20appeal%2C%20harmoniously%20blending%20classic%20and%20contemporary%20elements.%20The%20design%20not%20only%20pays%20homage%20to%20India's%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20but%20also%20creates%20a%20tranquil%20and%20inviting%20atmosphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20arrived%20at%20the%20Bandar%20Seri%20Begawan%20Airport%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20as%20he%20began%20his%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Brunei%20Darussalam%20-%20the%20first-ever%20bilateral%20trip%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM%20to%20the%20southeast%20Asian%20nation%20-%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Sultan%20Haji%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historic%20visit%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20coincides%20with%20the%2040th%20anniversary%20of%20establishment%20of%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Brunei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Inputs%20from%20IANS)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725378180000%2C%22vi