%20converting%20it%20into%20cryptocurrency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scamsters%20would%20post%20ads%20on%20social%20media%20apps%20like%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%20and%20X%20and%20try%20and%20lure%20people%20in%20by%20promising%20absurdly%20high%20returns.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20exactly%20what%20happened%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20Faridabad%2C%20who%20came%20across%20an%20ad%20on%20Facebook%20promising%20big%20returns%20from%20investments%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20After%20clicking%20on%20the%20link%2C%20she%20was%20added%20to%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20where%20she%20kept%20seeing%20success%20stories%20posted%20by%20other%20investors%2C%20who%20were%20actually%20members%20of%20the%20cyber%20fraud%20gang.%20The%20name%20of%20the%20group%20also%20had%20the%20name%20of%20a%20prominent%20bank%20in%20it%20to%20lend%20it%20legitimacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20all%20of%20this%2C%20she%20agreed%20to%20join%20another%20group%20and%20was%20instructed%20by%20the%20administrator%20to%20install%20an%20app%20called%20%26quot%3BIC%20Organ%20Max%26quot%3B%2C%20through%20which%20she%20%26quot%3Binvested%26quot%3B%20Rs%2061%20lakh.%20She%20was%20then%20told%20to%20install%20another%20app%20named%20%26quot%3BTechstars.shop%26quot%3B.%20The%20apps%20had%20the%20names%20of%20popular%20stocks%2C%20futures%2C%20options%20and%20other%20investment%20instruments%20for%20victims%20to%20put%20their%20money%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20build%20further%20trust%2C%20the%20victim%20might%20initially%20be%20shown%20to%20have%20got%20good%20returns%2C%20but%20in%20fact%20they%20are%20just%20numbers%20shown%20on%20these%20fake%20apps.%20While%20the%20victims%20invest%20more%20funds%2C%20they%20gradually%20realise%20that%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20withdraw%20their%20funds.%20When%20they%20try%20to%20take%20out%20their%20money%2C%20the%20scammer%20asks%20the%20victims%20to%20pay%20statutory%20taxes%2C%20brokerage%20fees%2C%20etc.%20which%20are%20nothing%20but%20ways%20to%20extract%20even%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20scammers%20believe%20that%20they%20have%20extracted%20as%20much%20money%20as%20possible%2C%20they%20cut%20off%20all%20communication%20and%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20from%20Faridabad%20had%20lost%20Rs%207.59%20crore%20before%20she%20realised%20she%20was%20being%20conned.%20The%20gang%20also%20cheated%20a%20Noida%20businessman%20of%20Rs%209.09%20crore%20and%20a%20Bhatinda%20doctor%20of%20Rs%205.93%20crore%20using%20the%20same%20method.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20arrests%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20conducted%20searches%20at%20multiple%20locations%20and%20traced%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20worth%20over%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20The%20money%20was%20routed%20using%20%26quot%3Bmule%26quot%3B%20bank%20accounts%2C%20which%20were%20also%20rented%20using%20chat%20apps.%20Transactions%20under%20Rs%205%20lakh%20were%20made%20in%20the%20accounts%20to%20avoid%20raising%20suspicion%20and%20the%20money%20was%20converted%20into%20cryptocurrency%20to%20be%20managed%20from%20overseas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725377640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F43at22o8_hacker-generic-cybercrime-generic-cyber-scam-generic_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffake-apps-investors-and-stocks-scamsters-con-faridabad-woman-of-rs-7-crore-6483057%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20con%20began%20with%20fake%20investors%2C%20then%20expanded%20to%20fake%20apps%20where%20people%20were%20urged%20to%20invest%20in%20fake%20stocks%20for%20high%20returns%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20they%20had%20been%20stripped%20of%20their%20life%20savings.%20A%20woman%20from%20Faridabad%20was%20cheated%20of%20over%20Rs%207%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3