Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmobile-phone-use-doesnt-increase-brain-cancer-risk-says-rsearch-review-13209113%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmobile-phone-use-doesnt-increase-brain-cancer-risk-says-rsearch-review-13209113%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Cites%20%26quot%3BLive-In%20Relationship%20Agreement%26quot%3B%20To%20Get%20Bail%20In%20Rape%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETo%20secure%20pre-arrest%20bail%20in%20a%20rape%20case%20filed%20by%20his%20partner%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20a%2046-year-old%20man%20has%20produced%20a%20%26quot%3Blive-in%20relationship%20agreement%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20claims%20states%20that%20they%20would%20not%20file%20any%20case%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20granted%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20rape%20case%20on%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20woman%20who%20took%20him%20to%20court%20told%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20that%20the%20signature%20on%20the%20document%20was%20not%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20works%20as%20a%20caregiver%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20while%20the%20accused%20is%20a%20government%20employee%2C%20said%20the%20police%2C%20which%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20verify%20the%20so-called%20relationship%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20alleged%20that%20her%20partner%20had%20promised%20to%20marry%20her%20and%20had%20raped%20her%20multiple%20times%20during%20the%20time%20they%20were%20living%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20accused%20has%20called%20it%20a%20case%20of%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20applicant%20has%20been%20falsely%20implicated%20in%20the%20case.%20He%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20circumstances.%20They%20were%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship.%20The%20agreement%20shows%20that%20both%20of%20them%20had%20agreed%20to%20be%20in%20a%20relationship.%20The%20agreement%20was%20made%2C%20the%20woman%20signed%20it.%20The%20agreement%20shows%20that%20both%20of%20them%20had%20agreed%20to%20be%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sunil%20Pandey%2C%20the%20man's%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Official%20Agreement%20Between%20Them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20seven-point%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20they%20will%20stay%20together%20from%20August%201%202024%20to%20June%2030%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20clause%20states%20that%20during%20this%20period%20they%20will%20not%20file%20any%20case%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20each%20other%20and%20will%20spend%20their%20time%20together%20peacefully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20will%20live%20with%20the%20man%20at%20his%20home%2C%20says%20the%20third%20clause%2C%20and%20if%20she%20finds%20his%20behavior%20inappropriate%2C%20they%20can%20separate%20at%20any%20time%20after%20giving%20one%20month's%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelatives%20of%20the%20woman%20cannot%20come%20to%20her%20house%20while%20she%20is%20staying%20with%20him%2C%20says%20the%20fourth%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20fifth%20clause%2C%20the%20woman%20should%20not%20cause%20any%20harassment%20or%20mental%20agony%20to%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20woman%20gets%20pregnant%20during%20this%20period%2C%20the%20man%20should%20not%20be%20held%20responsible%2C%20says%20the%20sixth%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seventh%20clause%20states%20that%20if%20the%20harassment%20causes%20mental%20trauma%20to%20the%20man%2C%20thereby%20ruining%20his%20life%2C%20the%20woman%20will%20be%20held%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725373440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fv2hdne1o_live-in-agreement-1200_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cites-live-in-relationship-agreement-to-get-bai