Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20Heritage%20Welfare%20Foundation%20in%20a%20statement%20called%20the%20drone%20attacks%20%26quot%3Ba%20clear%20act%20of%20terror%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20drones%20and%20sophisticated%20weapons%20previously%20unseen%20in%20this%20conflict%20demonstrates%20the%20militants'%20intent%20to%20inflict%20maximum%20harm%20and%20terrorise%20the%20Meitei%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20civil%20society%20group%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20latest%20Kuki%20militants'%20attack%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20case%2C%20but%20a%20pattern%20they%20have%20adopted%20over%20the%20last%20one%20year%20to%20escalate%20violence%2C%20to%20advance%20their%20openly%20declared%20goal%20of%20breaking%20up%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20reaction%20to%20the%20incidents%20that%20began%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20today%20called%20the%20attacks%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20of%20terrorism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20between%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20that%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725372300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fs3guc2q8_drone_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%2