t%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20unit%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecover%20clean%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20aluminium%20coatings%20for%20reuse%2C%20recover%20hazardous%20ink%20waste%20for%20reuse%20and%20upcycled%20fibrous%20agricultural%20wastes%20to%20create%20paper%20pulp%20that%20can%20be%20made%20into%20high-strength%20paper%20used%20for%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vinay%2C%20Founder%20of%20Indic%20Initiatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20chartered%20accountant%20by%20education%2C%20Vinay%20is%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20who%20started%20Indic%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20indigenous%20innovations%20that%20will%20benefit%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20machine%20works%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FTransformation-gif-1-1725015809.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363610%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20paper%20cups%2C%20tetra%20packs%20or%20tissues%20are%20received%2C%20they%20are%20manually%20put%20inside%20the%20recycling%20machine.%20The%20components%20go%20through%20a%20three-stage%20process.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20tetra%20packs%2C%20the%20machine%20uses%20a%20chemical%20suspension%20to%20separate%20it%20into%20aluminium%2C%20plastic%20and%20pulp.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20paper%20cups%2C%20it%20is%20separated%20into%20plastic%20and%20pulp.%20The%20pulp%20is%20then%20converted%20into%20pulp%20boards%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Seetharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20pulp%20boards%20are%20sold%20as%20