0challenging%20yet%20rewarding%20journey%2C%20transforming%20former%20agricultural%20land%20into%20a%20flourishing%20forest%20by%20removing%20non-native%20species.%20Their%20goal%20was%20simple%3A%20to%20create%20a%20forest%20exactly%20as%20nature%20intended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20have%20they%20succeeded%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99ve%20exceeded%20expectations.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20created%20the%20first%20biosphere%20reserve%20in%20India%20where%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20is%20minimal%2C%20time%20seems%20to%20stand%20still%2C%20and%20nature%20takes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Chowkidar%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20forest%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20completed%20his%20education%20in%20finance%20and%20environmental%20science%20at%20The%20Wharton%20School.%20After%20running%20successful%20businesses%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202010%20to%20continue%20his%20entrepreneurial%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20avid%20runner%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20major%20setback%20in%202013%20when%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20bronchial%20asthma%20while%20training%20for%20a%20marathon.%20This%20diagnosis%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20severe%20air%20pollution%2C%20ignited%20his%20passion%20for%20environmental%20issues.%20He%20became%20a%20leading%20advocate%20for%20air%20quality%20awareness%2C%20founding%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20movement%20%E2%80%98Our%20Right%20To%20Breathe%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Kr8tAy0D0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Kr8tAy0D0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F