e%20would%20be%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20a%20chowkidar%20(watchman)%20of%20the%20forests%20in%20India.%20I%20have%20no%20hope%20of%20better%20living%20conditions%20in%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20The%20air%20is%20toxic%20everywhere.%20I%20want%20to%20improve%20my%20own%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20living%20with%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jai%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20he%20often%20visited%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20affection%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20settle%2C%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20area%20that%20had%20become%20almost%20a%20second%20home%20to%20him%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai's%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi