0after%20reading%20multiple%20news%20articles%20that%20highlighted%20the%20perils%20of%20consuming%20chemical-laden%20vegetables%20that%20dominated%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20an%20unknown%20fact%20that%20chemical-laden%20vegetables%20are%20detrimental%20to%20human%20health.%20I%20thought%20just%20by%20sparing%20some%20time%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening%2C%20I%20could%20get%20healthy%20nutritious%20and%20chemical-free%20food%20for%20my%20family.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20did%20not%20like%20the%20taste%20of%20food%20cooked%20using%20vegetables%20I%20bought%20from%20the%20market.%20So%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20grow%20my%20own%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20transitioned%20to%20growing%20a%20variety%20of%20essential%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20chillies%2C%20cherry%20tomatoes%2C%20beans%2C%20cucumbers%2C%20brinjals%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20cauliflowers%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20more.%20With%20over%20200%20plants%20thriving%20in%20grow%20bags%2C%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348771%2Fgrow-organic-food-doctor-naveen-kumar-farming-workshop-chennai-vegetables-fruits-at-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20terrace%20garden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20joy%20and%20sustenance%20for%20Padma%3B%20and%20also%20a%20link%20to%20her%20rural%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20have%20to%20purchase%20potatoes%2C%20garlic%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20onions%20from%20the%20market.%20Other%20than%20these%20vegetables%2C%20my%20terrace%20garden%20supplies%20all%20the%20basic%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3