rystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362467%2Fbest-seafood-restaurants-goa-martins-corner-vinayak-souza-lobo-sharada-bar-coquiero-bhumiputra-fat-fish%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Fight%20Crime%20With%20AI%3A%20IPS%20Officer%20Explains%20How%20Maharashtra%20Police%E2%80%99s%20MARVEL%20Will%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20can%20predict%20wars.%20Sounds%20unbelievable%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaven%20Sentry%2C%20an%20American%20AI%20tool%2C%20was%20able%20to%20predict%20Taliban%20attacks%20in%20Afghanistan.%20An%20Economist%20report%20states%20that%20the%20model%20had%20achieved%2070%25%20accuracy%20by%20October%202020.%20Since%20then%2C%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20across%20the%20world%20have%20turned%20to%20AI%20to%20help%20understand%20patterns%20and%20build%20indicators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20of%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20the%20state%20police%20force%20perform%20their%20duties%20more%20efficiently.%20This%20will%20be%20done%20through%20Maharashtra%20Research%20and%20Vigilance%20for%20Enhanced%20Law%20Enforcement%20(MARVEL)%2C%20a%20separate%20entity%2C%20created%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStated%20to%20be%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20country%2C%20this%20initiative%20is%20dedicated%20solely%20to%20the%20integration%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20into%20law%20enforcement.%20The%20entity%E2%80%99s%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20develop%20AI%20tools%20tailored%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20various%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20within%20the%20state.%20These%20tools%20are%20not%20just%20generic%20solutions%20but%20are%20tailor-made%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20requirements%20of%20different%20police%20departments.%20They%20will%20improve%20crime%20prediction%20and%20enable%20speedy%20resolution%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%20will%20be%20used%20for%20various%20critical%20applications%20%E2%80%93%20from%20missing%20persons%2C%20hit%20and%20runs%20to%20organised%20crime%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujata%20Saunik%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20states%20that%20the%20mission%20is%20to%20use%20the%20latest%20AI%20tools%20on%20crime%20data%20to%20speed%20up%20investigations%2C%20leading%20to%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20how%20this%20AI%20tool%20can%20possibly%20change%20the%20way%20cases%20are%20handled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%20humans%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%20is%20a%20Special%20Purpose%20Vehicle%20(SPV)%2C%20formed%20through%20a%20tripartite%20agreement%20between%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)-Nagpur%20and%20Pinaka%20Technologies%20Private%20Limited.%20It%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarssh%20Poddar%2C%20SP%20of%20Nagpur%20Rural%20and%20ex-officio%20Director%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20MARVEL%20spoke%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20about%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201542px)%20100vw%2C%201542px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harssh%20Poddar%2C%20SP%20of%20Nagpur%20Rural%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%201542w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362915%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarssh%20Poddar%2C%20SP%20of%20Nagpur%20Rural%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20home%20department%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270164%2Fips-officer-arti-singh-is-only-woman-commissioner-of-police-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduce%20AI%20into%20law%20enforcement%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20largely%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20data%20analytics%20and%20pattern%20detection.%20Police%20or%20any%20law%20enforcement%20agency%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20data%2C%20which%20can%20be%20suggestive%20of%20various%20patterns.%20Studying%20these%20patterns%20can%20help%20in%20crime%20prevention%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Harssh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20mission%20of%20MARVEL%20is%20to%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20human%20law%20enforcement.%20Seasoned%20officers%2C%20like%20head%20constables%20or%20inspectors%2C%20assess%20large%20volumes%20of%20data%20and%20provide%20valuable%20insights%20based%20on%20the%20patterns%20they%20recognise.%20This%20entity%20would%20perform%20these%20tasks%20too%2C%20once%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20data%20has%20been%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20proliferation%20of%20technology%20in%20urban%20spaces%E2%80%94such%20as%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20mobile%20phones%2C%20which%20frequently%20capture%20photos%20and%20videos%E2%80%94many%20crimes%20are%20now%20recorded%20digitally.%20AI%20algorithms%20can%20analyse%20this%20visual%20data%20to%20predict%20and%20prevent%20crimes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20detect%20them%20after%20they%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20an%20example%20of%20chain%20snatching%20cases%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20rural%20SP%20states%20that%20the%20role%20of%20AI%20can%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAI%20might%20notice%20details%20in%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20that%20a%20human%20might%20miss%2C%20such%20as%20the%20specific%20make%20of%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20it%20travels%2C%20or%20the%20type%20of%20helmet%20used%20by%20the%20perpetrator.%20These%20subtle%20patterns%20can%20be%20crucial%20in%20solving%20cases%20and%20preventing%20future%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20states%20too%20might%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20augment%20law%20enforcement%2C%20Maharashtra%20might%20be%20the%20first%20to%20create%20an%20independent%20entity%20for%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20role%20of%20MARVEL%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20solutions%20on%20a%20case%20to%20case%20basis.%20Instead%2C%20it%20focuses%20on%20developing%20tools%20and%20algorithms%20that%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20can%20deploy%20in%20their%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284171%2Fpolice-inspector-teaches-poor-children-ayodhya-inspiration-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagpur%20Rural%20SP%20%3C%2Fa%3Estates%20that%20if%20a%20particular%20police%20team%20wants%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20deal%20with%20cases%20of%20missing%20people%2C%20and%20share%20their%20requirements%2C%20MARVEL%20would%20design%20it%20and%20share%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20an%20investigative%20agency%20that%20is%20providing%20help%20with%20particular%20cases.%20We%20would%20design%20a%20tool%20depending%20upon%20the%20requirement%20of%20the%20other%20agency%20and%20then%20we%20would%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20stresses%20Harrsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20can%20solve%20complex%20crimes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20MARVEL%20is%20working%20on%20five%20different%20projects%20for%20as%20many%20agencies.%20It%20has%2025%20technical%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20AI%20tools%20will%20be%20able%20to%20layer%20data%20and%20give%20a%20fair%20sense%20of%20what%20might%20have%20happened.%20It%20would%20give%20predictive%20modelling%20solutions%2C%20which%20officials%20will%20then%20have%20to%20interpret.%20It%20will%20show%20you%20trends%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Sujata%20Saunik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%